Long-time Spanish Commentary legend, Carlos Cabrera, has joined All Elite Wrestling. This comes after AEW social media announced that Cabrera was “All Elite".”

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b612b46d-ff3a-48e0-aa52-e5db6a308410/436303043_122102506652282121_954091696279198154_n.jpg)

Carlos Cabrera is known for being WWE’s Spanish commentator from 1993 until 2022. He was the Spanish announcer for every WrestleMania from WrestleMania X until WrestleMania 37. He’d reunite with long-time commentary partner Hugo Savinovich on Lucha Libre AAA Worldwide during the Rey de Reyes 2022 event.